812
00:41:31,208 --> 00:41:34,000
I'm not going to win
this one, am I, Chief?

813
00:41:36,208 --> 00:41:38,542
No, sir.

814
00:41:45,041 --> 00:41:47,417
<i>Captain's Log, supplemental.</i>

815
00:41:47,458 --> 00:41:50,041
<i>Captain Maxwell has turned his</i>
<i>ship over to his First Officer</i>

816
00:41:50,083 --> 00:41:52,083
<i>and transported</i>
<i>aboard the</i> Enterprise.

817
00:41:52,125 --> 00:41:56,041
<i>I have confined him to quarters</i>
<i>for the return voyage.</i>

818
00:41:56,083 --> 00:41:58,083
Thank you, Chief.

819
00:42:00,166 --> 00:42:02,583
I'd just like
to say, sir

820
00:42:02,625 --> 00:42:04,375
he was a good man.

821
00:42:04,417 --> 00:42:05,959
What he did was
terribly wrong

822
00:42:06,000 --> 00:42:07,375
I know that now

823
00:42:07,417 --> 00:42:10,583
but I'm still proud
to have served with him.

824
00:42:10,625 --> 00:42:12,834
Thank you, Chief.

825
00:42:12,875 --> 00:42:14,959
And well done.

826
00:42:15,000 --> 00:42:16,917
That'll be all.

827
00:42:20,208 --> 00:42:23,792
Well, his loyalty is admirable

828
00:42:23,834 --> 00:42:26,667
even if it is misplaced.

829
00:42:29,208 --> 00:42:32,000
The loyalty that you would
so quickly dismiss

830
00:42:32,041 --> 00:42:35,375
does not come easily
to my people, Gul Macet.

831
00:42:35,417 --> 00:42:37,959
You have much to learn
about us.

832
00:42:38,000 --> 00:42:40,709
Benjamin Maxwell
<i>earned</i> the loyalty

833
00:42:40,750 --> 00:42:42,667
of those who served
with him.

834
00:42:43,875 --> 00:42:48,709
You know, in war,
he was twice honored

835
00:42:48,750 --> 00:42:51,375
with the Federation's
highest citation

836
00:42:51,417 --> 00:42:54,083
for courage
and valor.

837
00:42:54,125 --> 00:42:58,291
And if he could not find
a role for himself in peace

838
00:42:58,333 --> 00:43:03,667
we can pity him, but we
shall not dismiss him.

839
00:43:03,709 --> 00:43:06,792
You are welcome to
your opinion, Captain.

840
00:43:06,834 --> 00:43:12,333
I, for one, am grateful
he is under lock and key.

841
00:43:12,375 --> 00:43:15,041
One more thing,
Gul Macet.

842
00:43:16,500 --> 00:43:19,458
Maxwell was right.

843
00:43:19,500 --> 00:43:23,417
