scientific equipment, were they?

844
00:43:23,458 --> 00:43:27,208
A research station
within arm's reach

845
00:43:27,250 --> 00:43:29,917
of three Federation sectors?

846
00:43:29,959 --> 00:43:31,667
Cargo ships running

847
00:43:31,709 --> 00:43:33,875
with high-energy
subspace fields

848
00:43:33,917 --> 00:43:36,750
that jam sensors?

849
00:43:36,792 --> 00:43:39,166
If you believe
the transport ship

850
00:43:39,208 --> 00:43:41,458
was carrying
weapons, Captain

851
00:43:41,500 --> 00:43:43,166
why didn't you board it

852
00:43:43,208 --> 00:43:45,875
as Maxwell
requested?

853
00:43:47,000 --> 00:43:50,083
I was here
to protect the peace--

854
00:43:50,125 --> 00:43:53,583
a peace that I firmly believe
is in the interest

855
00:43:53,625 --> 00:43:55,750
of both
our peoples.

856
00:43:55,792 --> 00:43:57,792
If I had attempted
to board that ship

857
00:43:57,834 --> 00:43:59,250
I'm quite certain that you and I

858
00:43:59,291 --> 00:44:02,500
would not be having
this pleasant conversation

859
00:44:02,542 --> 00:44:07,000
and that ships on both sides
would now be arming for war.

860
00:44:07,041 --> 00:44:09,375
Captain, I assure you...

861
00:44:09,417 --> 00:44:12,417
Take this message
to your leaders, Gul Macet.

862
00:44:12,458 --> 00:44:16,041
We'll be watching.
